Case 1:21-cr-00330-DAD-NR Document 149-2 Filed 06/29/22 Page 12 of 12

IV. Conclusion
Defendant Ghislaine Maxwell's third motion for release on bail, Dkt. No. 160, is DENIED. The parties are ORDERED to meet and confer and justify any redactions by March 24, 2021. If they conclude that redactions are unnecessary, the Defendant is ORDERED to docket the unredacted version of the brief by March 24, 2021.
SO ORDERED.
Dated: March 22, 2021 New York, New York
ALISON J. NATHAN
United States District Judge
